Personal Rating:
7/10 - Sucker for cute art and doxxed team but dislike the closed discord. Would be minting if I had a spot but alas I do not. Watching this mint day and joining the raffle!

Summary:
- Strong team, Fun idea, Cute artwork, degens will love it
- Moderately bullish on this project due to a strong team and interesting, fun idea with the party mechanic. - The fact that itâ€™s gasless as well and requires only a wallet signature is pretty sweet!

Hype & Community:
- Hype with it being near impossible to get into discord. 
- This would be the only thing I ding them down on as I am not a fan of projects locking discords as canâ€™t gauge inner community.
- Decent organic looking growth on twitter that doesnâ€™t look botted IMO

Utility:
- You can join their parties and get a chance to roll some rare traits. 
- Parties are gasless and only require wallet signing
- Fun gambling game all the degens will love!

Roadmap: 
- No roadmap apparent. To quote the site â€œNo bs, no promises, no buzzwords. Just fun.â€
- Usually a red flag but with a strong team and a fun initial idea I can dig it.
- May have other ideas up their sleeve after the mint

Art:
- Simple, cute art. 
- Has potential to stand out as a pfp - bright colors
- Unique concept where traits can be added (metadata updated) if you take your duck to the parties

Founders & Team:
- Team mostly doxxed
- Proven artist with huge loyal following (788K IG) @thegalshir
- Tech lead has strong background in dev/software industry @jishai
- Experienced music composer (Maybe for the parties?) @RafaelFrost
